ukwe, 40, for  allegedly beating his 40-year-old wife, Glory Madukwe to death. September 13, 2019 In "News" A 37-year-old man, Ifeanyi Ajaero, has been arrested by men of Ogun State Police Command for allegedly tying his 28-year-old wife, Obiageli, to a generator from night till daybreak. April 16, 2017 In "News" A 47-year-old woman, Mrs Joy Egeonu, has been arrested for beating her husband’s 11-year-old nephew to death, for allegedly stealing N6,500 in Agbado area of Ogun State. February 7, 2019 In "Crime Guard"